        "subject": "LU-10048 ofd: take local locks within transaction",
        "message": "LU-10048 ofd: take local locks within transaction\n\nthe patch (along with osd companion) addresses long outstanding\ntechnical debt resulting in different locking order on MDT and\nOST. with OUT introduction this mismatch began to result in\ndeadlocks as OUT is used by the both sides and can't easily\nsupport two different locking models simultanously.\n\nChange-Id: I1eaeb58ae3d61869914293a9fea2d0a1faefe76b\nSigned-off-by: Alex Zhuravlev <bzzz@whamcloud.com>\n"
